product.description:
Stay one step ahead in the kitchen with assistive cooking methods that provide a groundbreaking smart experience and new levels of precision that help bring out the boldness in every flavor. Assisted Cook Cycles recommend the ideal cooking cycle and temperature for common foods like cake, salmon filets, roasted vegetables, and more. Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking and roasting. Temperature Probe provides internal temperature updates on oven screen without opening the door.Backlit knobs twist to navigate cook cycles and customize home screen.

Features:

  • Knob and touch controls are easy to use
  • Enjoy the convenience of self-cleaning
  • Convection baking provides even heat distribution for improved browning and crisping
  • Wall oven is certified for UL
  • Oven includes baking element, air fry, meat thermometer, steam cooking, and viewing window
  • Sabbath Mode to meet kosher requirements for use on the Jewish Sabbath and other religious holidays
  • Smooth close door makes it easy to close the oven while your hands are full with special hinges that help prevent slamming
  • FIT System Limited Guarantee
  • Assisted cooking modes suggest cook times and temperatures on an easy-to-navigate touch screen so you can explore new recipes with confidence
  • Temperature probe provides internal temperature updates on oven screen or your mobile device so you can keep the precise heat needed
  • Favorites make your favorite cooking settings easy to access by creating and saving them right in the KitchenAid™ App or directly on your appliance
  • Far View screen automatically enlarges key information like temperature or remaining time after a few minutes of inactivity
  • Covered under a 1 year parts and labor manufacturer warranty

Product Technologies:

  • Even-Heat™ True Convection: Features a unique bow-tie design with a heating element and fan that circulates hot air throughout the entire oven, providing optimal temperatures for delicious baked goods, juicy roasts and flavorful vegetables
  • Steam Bake with Tray: Adds moisture during the baking process so you can enjoy Basque cheesecake, or fluffy, moist honey wheat sandwich bread
  • Fresh Pizza Mode: Create homemade, restaurant-style pizzas from the comfort of your kitchen. Fresh pizza mode cranks the heat to 550°F for delicious results
  • No Preheat Slow Roast: Provides tender meats, pastas and much more without the hassle of a separate appliance. Plus high-temp settings for soups, medium-temp settings for braising meats and low-temp settings to keep food warm after cooking
  • SatinGlide™ Roll-Out Extension Rack: Features a roll-out extension rack and ball-bearing rollers with an easy-grip handle for effortless loading and unloading of large or heavy dishes
  • Slow Cook: Cooks food slowly at a low temperature, great for stewing meats and vegetables or building flavors in stews and currys with temperatures from 180°F to 300°F
  • No Preheat Air Fry Mode: Uses heating elements and a fan to circulate hot air within the cavity, crisping and browning food with less oil. When compared to deep frying. Dishwasher-safe basket sold separately
  • Steam Clean: Perfect for quick, routine maintenance, helps loosen cooked-on food in under an hour. Simply add water to the bottom of the oven and wipe down after the cycle
  • Self-Clean: For a deeper clean, the high-temperature Self-Clean Cycle powers through baked-on spills, leaving the oven cavity clean with just a final wipe-down

Specifications:

  • Convection: Yes
  • Self Cleaning: Yes
  • Depth: 26-15/16"
  • Height: 28-3/4"
  • Width: 29-3/4"
  • Cutout Depth: 24"
  • Cutout Height: 28"
  • Cutout Width: 28-1/2"

  • No Preheat Slow Roast: Provides tender meats, pastas and much more without the hassle of a separate appliance. Plus high-temp settings for soups, medium-temp settings for braising meats and low-temp settings to keep food warm after cooking
  • SatinGlide™ Roll-Out Extension Rack: Features a roll-out extension rack and ball-bearing rollers with an easy-grip handle for effortless loading and unloading of large or heavy dishes
  • Slow Cook: Cooks food slowly at a low temperature, great for stewing meats and vegetables or building flavors in stews and currys with temperatures from 180°F to 300°F
  • No Preheat Air Fry Mode: Uses heating elements and a fan to circulate hot air within the cavity, crisping and browning food with less oil. When compared to deep frying. Dishwasher-safe basket sold separately
  • Steam Clean: Perfect for quick, routine maintenance, helps loosen cooked-on food in under an hour. Simply add water to the bottom of the oven and wipe down after the cycle
  • Self-Clean: For a deeper clean, the high-temperature Self-Clean Cycle powers through baked-on spills, leaving the oven cavity clean with just a final wipe-down

Specifications:

  • Convection: Yes
  • Self Cleaning: Yes

  • Height: 28-3/4"
  • Width: 29-3/4"
  • Cutout Depth: 24"
  • Cutout Height: 28"
  • Cutout Width: 28-1/2"

rawPayload.Product_Description_Web_Retailer: Explore new recipes with built-in tips on this KitchenAid smart wall oven, featuring our Most Precise Even-Heat(TM) True Convection and Assisted Cooking Modes. LED Touchscreen display and backlit knobs allow for tactile display navigation. The backlit knobs also provide a visual cue throughout the cooking process, illuminating when the oven is preheating and pulsing when cooking is finished. Designed to be personalized, these wall ovens are available in a curated palette of exterior finishes and can be customized with mixed metal hardware.
rawPayload.Product_Title_Web_Retailer: 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes - PrintShield(TM) Finish

Primary_Attributes.Description_Verified: Stay one step ahead in the kitchen with the Kitchen. Aid 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven. Featuring Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking, a temperature probe for precise cooking, and innovative cooking modes like Air Fry and Steam Bake. This oven is designed for the modern cook, offering a touchscreen display, backlit knobs, and smart home compatibility for a seamless cooking experience.
Primary_Attributes.Product_Title_Verified: KitchenAid 30" Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes - Printshield™ Finish
Primary_Attributes.Details_Verified: This KitchenAid wall oven brings modern technology into the kitchen, designed to help you explore new recipes with ease. Features include Assisted Cooking Modes, Even-Heat™ True Convection, and a temperature probe for precise cooking results. The sleek PrintShield™ finish resists fingerprints and smudges, making cleanup a breeze.
Primary_Attributes.Features_List_HTML:
• Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking
  • Temperature probe for precise cooking
  • Assisted Cooking Modes for culinary exploration
  • PrintShield™ Finish resists fingerprints and smudges
  • Smart home compatible for a seamless cooking experience
  • Air Fry and Steam Bake modes for versatile cooking
  • Self-Cleaning and Steam Clean options for easy maintenance
  • Backlit knobs and touchscreen display for easy navigation
  • Sabbath Mode to meet kosher requirements
  • Fit System Limited Guarantee for a perfect fit in your kitchen

openai.value: KitchenAid 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes - PrintShield™ Finish

xai.value: KitchenAid 30-Inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Even-Heat™ True Convection and Fresh Pizza Mode

product_title.final_value: KitchenAid 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes - PrintShield™ Finish

description.final_value: Stay ahead in the kitchen with the KitchenAid 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven. It features Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking, a temperature probe for precise cooking, and smart capabilities for assisted cooking modes. The oven's self-cleaning feature and air fry mode offer convenience, while the PrintShield™ Finish resists fingerprints. Customize your appliance with backlit knobs and explore new recipes with confidence.

details.final_value: This KitchenAid wall oven brings smart technology and culinary precision into your kitchen. Its Even-Heat™ True Convection system ensures even baking, and the temperature probe allows for precise temperature monitoring. The oven's smart capabilities enable assisted cooking modes, making it easier to try new recipes. The PrintShield™ Finish keeps the oven looking new by resisting fingerprints and smudges.

features_list.final_value:
• Even-heat™ true convection for consistent baking
  • Self-cleaning feature for easy maintenance
  • Air fry mode for healthier cooking
  • Temperature probe for precise cooking
  • Smart capabilities with assisted cooking modes
  • Printshield™ finish resists fingerprints
  • Backlit knobs for easy control and visibility
  • Sabbath mode for religious observances
  • Steam bake with tray for moist baking
  • Fit system limited guarantee for a perfect fit
  • Even-heat true convection for uniform baking and roasting
  • Assisted cooking modes suggest optimal times and temperatures
  • Air fry function for crispy results with less oil
  • Smart connectivity with amazon alexa and google assistant
  • Self-cleaning cycle for easy maintenance
  • Temperature probe monitors internal food temperature
  • Fingerprint-resistant finish for a clean look
  • Steam bake option for moist baking results
  • Fresh pizza mode reaches up to 550°f

Assisted Cook Cycles recommend the ideal cooking cycle and temperature for common foods like cake, salmon filets, roasted vegetables, and more. Temperature Probe provides internal temperature updates on oven screen without opening the door.Backlit knobs twist to navigate cook cycles and customize home screen.
corrections_made.correctedValue: This KitchenAid smart electric single wall oven offers precise cooking with Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent results. Features include assisted cooking modes, air fry capability, and a temperature probe for monitoring food without opening the door. With a fingerprint-resistant stainless steel finish and intuitive touchscreen controls, it's designed for modern kitchens. Enjoy easy cleaning with self-clean and steam options, plus smart integration with Alexa and Google Assistant.

product.description:
Stay one step ahead in the kitchen with assistive cooking methods that provide a groundbreaking smart experience and new levels of precision that help bring out the boldness in every flavor. Assisted Cook Cycles recommend the ideal cooking cycle and temperature for common foods like cake, salmon filets, roasted vegetables, and more. Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking and roasting. Temperature Probe provides internal temperature updates on oven screen without opening the door.Backlit knobs twist to navigate cook cycles and customize home screen.

Features:

  • Knob and touch controls are easy to use
  • Enjoy the convenience of self-cleaning
  • Convection baking provides even heat distribution for improved browning and crisping
  • Wall oven is certified for UL
  • Oven includes baking element, air fry, meat thermometer, steam cooking, and viewing window
  • Sabbath Mode to meet kosher requirements for use on the Jewish Sabbath and other religious holidays
  • Smooth close door makes it easy to close the oven while your hands are full with special hinges that help prevent slamming
  • FIT System Limited Guarantee
  • Assisted cooking modes suggest cook times and temperatures on an easy-to-navigate touch screen so you can explore new recipes with confidence
  • Temperature probe provides internal temperature updates on oven screen or your mobile device so you can keep the precise heat needed
  • Favorites make your favorite cooking settings easy to access by creating and saving them right in the KitchenAid™ App or directly on your appliance
  • Far View screen automatically enlarges key information like temperature or remaining time after a few minutes of inactivity
  • Covered under a 1 year parts and labor manufacturer warranty

Product Technologies:

  • Even-Heat™ True Convection: Features a unique bow-tie design with a heating element and fan that circulates hot air throughout the entire oven, providing optimal temperatures for delicious baked goods, juicy roasts and flavorful vegetables
  • Steam Bake with Tray: Adds moisture during the baking process so you can enjoy Basque cheesecake, or fluffy, moist honey wheat sandwich bread
  • Fresh Pizza Mode: Create homemade, restaurant-style pizzas from the comfort of your kitchen. Fresh pizza mode cranks the heat to 550°F for delicious results
  • No Preheat Slow Roast: Provides tender meats, pastas and much more without the hassle of a separate appliance. Plus high-temp settings for soups, medium-temp settings for braising meats and low-temp settings to keep food warm after cooking
  • SatinGlide™ Roll-Out Extension Rack: Features a roll-out extension rack and ball-bearing rollers with an easy-grip handle for effortless loading and unloading of large or heavy dishes
  • Slow Cook: Cooks food slowly at a low temperature, great for stewing meats and vegetables or building flavors in stews and currys with temperatures from 180°F to 300°F
  • No Preheat Air Fry Mode: Uses heating elements and a fan to circulate hot air within the cavity, crisping and browning food with less oil. When compared to deep frying. Dishwasher-safe basket sold separately
  • Steam Clean: Perfect for quick, routine maintenance, helps loosen cooked-on food in under an hour. Simply add water to the bottom of the oven and wipe down after the cycle
  • Self-Clean: For a deeper clean, the high-temperature Self-Clean Cycle powers through baked-on spills, leaving the oven cavity clean with just a final wipe-down

Specifications:

  • Convection: Yes
  • Self Cleaning: Yes
  • Depth: 26-15/16"
  • Height: 28-3/4"
  • Width: 29-3/4"
  • Cutout Depth: 24"
  • Cutout Height: 28"
  • Cutout Width: 28-1/2"

rawPayload.Product_Description_Web_Retailer: Explore new recipes with built-in tips on this KitchenAid smart wall oven, featuring our Most Precise Even-Heat(TM) True Convection and Assisted Cooking Modes. LED Touchscreen display and backlit knobs allow for tactile display navigation. The backlit knobs also provide a visual cue throughout the cooking process, illuminating when the oven is preheating and pulsing when cooking is finished. Designed to be personalized, these wall ovens are available in a curated palette of exterior finishes and can be customized with mixed metal hardware.
rawPayload.Product_Title_Web_Retailer: 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes - PrintShield(TM) Finish

Primary_Attributes.Description_Verified: Experience precision cooking with Kitchen. Aid's 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven. Featuring Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking, Assisted Cooking Modes for culinary exploration, and a sleek Print. Shield™ finish. Control your oven through the Kitchen. Aid™ App or with voice commands using Amazon Alexa or Google Assistant for a seamless smart home integration.
Primary_Attributes.Product_Title_Verified: KitchenAid 30" Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes - Printshield™ Finish
Primary_Attributes.Details_Verified: This KitchenAid wall oven brings modern convenience to your kitchen with features like Air Fry, Steam Bake, and a Temperature Probe. Its smart capabilities allow for remote monitoring and control, making cooking more intuitive and enjoyable.
Primary_Attributes.Features_List_HTML:
• Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent results

description.final_value: Stay one step ahead in the kitchen with the KitchenAid 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven. Featuring Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking and roasting, Assisted Cooking Modes for built-in tips, and a smart experience with app compatibility. The LED Touchscreen and backlit knobs enhance usability, while the PrintShield™ Finish resists fingerprints. Customize your kitchen with its sleek design, available in a stainless steel finish.

details.final_value: This KitchenAid wall oven brings innovation to your kitchen with features like Even-Heat™ True Convection, Assisted Cooking Modes, and smart connectivity for a seamless cooking experience. Its PrintShield™ Finish adds a touch of elegance while making cleaning easier.

product.description:
Stay one step ahead in the kitchen with assistive cooking methods that provide a groundbreaking smart experience and new levels of precision that help bring out the boldness in every flavor. Assisted Cook Cycles recommend the ideal cooking cycle and temperature for common foods like cake, salmon filets, roasted vegetables, and more. Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking and roasting. Temperature Probe provides internal temperature updates on oven screen without opening the door.Backlit knobs twist to navigate cook cycles and customize home screen.

Features:

  • Knob and touch controls are easy to use
  • Enjoy the convenience of self-cleaning
  • Convection baking provides even heat distribution for improved browning and crisping
  • Wall oven is certified for UL
  • Oven includes baking element, air fry, meat thermometer, steam cooking, and viewing window
  • Sabbath Mode to meet kosher requirements for use on the Jewish Sabbath and other religious holidays
  • Smooth close door makes it easy to close the oven while your hands are full with special hinges that help prevent slamming
  • FIT System Limited Guarantee
  • Assisted cooking modes suggest cook times and temperatures on an easy-to-navigate touch screen so you can explore new recipes with confidence
  • Temperature probe provides internal temperature updates on oven screen or your mobile device so you can keep the precise heat needed
  • Favorites make your favorite cooking settings easy to access by creating and saving them right in the KitchenAid™ App or directly on your appliance
  • Far View screen automatically enlarges key information like temperature or remaining time after a few minutes of inactivity
  • Covered under a 1 year parts and labor manufacturer warranty

Product Technologies:

  • Even-Heat™ True Convection: Features a unique bow-tie design with a heating element and fan that circulates hot air throughout the entire oven, providing optimal temperatures for delicious baked goods, juicy roasts and flavorful vegetables
  • Steam Bake with Tray: Adds moisture during the baking process so you can enjoy Basque cheesecake, or fluffy, moist honey wheat sandwich bread
  • Fresh Pizza Mode: Create homemade, restaurant-style pizzas from the comfort of your kitchen. Fresh pizza mode cranks the heat to 550°F for delicious results
  • No Preheat Slow Roast: Provides tender meats, pastas and much more without the hassle of a separate appliance. Plus high-temp settings for soups, medium-temp settings for braising meats and low-temp settings to keep food warm after cooking
  • SatinGlide™ Roll-Out Extension Rack: Features a roll-out extension rack and ball-bearing rollers with an easy-grip handle for effortless loading and unloading of large or heavy dishes
  • Slow Cook: Cooks food slowly at a low temperature, great for stewing meats and vegetables or building flavors in stews and currys with temperatures from 180°F to 300°F
  • No Preheat Air Fry Mode: Uses heating elements and a fan to circulate hot air within the cavity, crisping and browning food with less oil. When compared to deep frying. Dishwasher-safe basket sold separately
  • Steam Clean: Perfect for quick, routine maintenance, helps loosen cooked-on food in under an hour. Simply add water to the bottom of the oven and wipe down after the cycle
  • Self-Clean: For a deeper clean, the high-temperature Self-Clean Cycle powers through baked-on spills, leaving the oven cavity clean with just a final wipe-down

Specifications:

  • Convection: Yes
  • Self Cleaning: Yes
  • Depth: 26-15/16"
  • Height: 28-3/4"
  • Width: 29-3/4"
  • Cutout Depth: 24"
  • Cutout Height: 28"
  • Cutout Width: 28-1/2"

rawPayload.Ferguson_Description:
Stay one step ahead in the kitchen with assistive cooking methods that provide a groundbreaking smart experience and new levels of precision that help bring out the boldness in every flavor. Assisted Cook Cycles recommend the ideal cooking cycle and temperature for common foods like cake, salmon filets, roasted vegetables, and more. Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking and roasting. Temperature Probe provides internal temperature updates on oven screen without opening the door.Backlit knobs twist to navigate cook cycles and customize home screen.

Features:

  • Knob and touch controls are easy to use
  • Enjoy the convenience of self-cleaning
  • Convection baking provides even heat distribution for improved browning and crisping
  • Wall oven is certified for UL
  • Oven includes baking element, air fry, meat thermometer, steam cooking, and viewing window
  • Sabbath Mode to meet kosher requirements for use on the Jewish Sabbath and other religious holidays
  • Smooth close door makes it easy to close the oven while your hands are full with special hinges that help prevent slamming
  • FIT System Limited Guarantee
  • Assisted cooking modes suggest cook times and temperatures on an easy-to-navigate touch screen so you can explore new recipes with confidence
  • Temperature probe provides internal temperature updates on oven screen or your mobile device so you can keep the precise heat needed
  • Favorites make your favorite cooking settings easy to access by creating and saving them right in the KitchenAid™ App or directly on your appliance
  • Far View screen automatically enlarges key information like temperature or remaining time after a few minutes of inactivity
  • Covered under a 1 year parts and labor manufacturer warranty

Product Technologies:

  • Even-Heat™ True Convection: Features a unique bow-tie design with a heating element and fan that circulates hot air throughout the entire oven, providing optimal temperatures for delicious baked goods, juicy roasts and flavorful vegetables
  • Steam Bake with Tray: Adds moisture during the baking process so you can enjoy Basque cheesecake, or fluffy, moist honey wheat sandwich bread
  • Fresh Pizza Mode: Create homemade, restaurant-style pizzas from the comfort of your kitchen. Fresh pizza mode cranks the heat to 550°F for delicious results
  • No Preheat Slow Roast: Provides tender meats, pastas and much more without the hassle of a separate appliance. Plus high-temp settings for soups, medium-temp settings for braising meats and low-temp settings to keep food warm after cooking
  • SatinGlide™ Roll-Out Extension Rack: Features a roll-out extension rack and ball-bearing rollers with an easy-grip handle for effortless loading and unloading of large or heavy dishes
  • Slow Cook: Cooks food slowly at a low temperature, great for stewing meats and vegetables or building flavors in stews and currys with temperatures from 180°F to 300°F
  • No Preheat Air Fry Mode: Uses heating elements and a fan to circulate hot air within the cavity, crisping and browning food with less oil. When compared to deep frying. Dishwasher-safe basket sold separately
  • Steam Clean: Perfect for quick, routine maintenance, helps loosen cooked-on food in under an hour. Simply add water to the bottom of the oven and wipe down after the cycle
  • Self-Clean: For a deeper clean, the high-temperature Self-Clean Cycle powers through baked-on spills, leaving the oven cavity clean with just a final wipe-down

Specifications:

  • Convection: Yes
  • Self Cleaning: Yes
  • Depth: 26-15/16"
  • Height: 28-3/4"
  • Width: 29-3/4"
  • Cutout Depth: 24"
  • Cutout Height: 28"
  • Cutout Width: 28-1/2"

rawPayload.Product_Description_Web_Retailer: Explore new recipes with built-in tips on this KitchenAid smart wall oven, featuring our Most Precise Even-Heat(TM) True Convection and Assisted Cooking Modes. LED Touchscreen display and backlit knobs allow for tactile display navigation. The backlit knobs also provide a visual cue throughout the cooking process, illuminating when the oven is preheating and pulsing when cooking is finished. Designed to be personalized, these wall ovens are available in a curated palette of exterior finishes and can be customized with mixed metal hardware.
rawPayload.Product_Title_Web_Retailer: 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes - PrintShield(TM) Finish

Primary_Attributes.Description_Verified: Experience precision cooking with Kitchen. Aid's 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven, featuring Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking and roasting. Explore new recipes with ease using the Assisted Cooking Modes and enjoy the convenience of a self-cleaning function. This oven is designed for modern kitchens, offering a sleek Print. Shield™ Finish that resists fingerprints and smudges.
Primary_Attributes.Product_Title_Verified: KitchenAid 30" Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes - Printshield™ Finish
Primary_Attributes.Details_Verified: This KitchenAid wall oven brings smart technology and culinary precision into your kitchen. It's equipped with advanced features like Air Fry, Steam Bake, and a Meat Thermometer, all controlLED through an intuitive LCD touch display. The oven's spacious 5 cu ft capacity and robust construction make it a versatile addition to your cooking arsenal.
Primary_Attributes.Features_List_HTML:
• Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking and roasting
  • Assisted Cooking Modes for culinary exploration
  • Self-cleaning function for easy maintenance
  • PrintShield™ Finish resists fingerprints and smudges
  • 5 cu ft capacity to handle large dishes
  • Steam Bake with Tray for moist and delicious bread
  • Fresh Pizza Mode for restaurant-style pizzas at home
  • Smart Appliance with connectivity features
  • Temperature Probe for precise cooking control
  • No Preheat Air Fry Mode for healthier cooking options

xai.value: KitchenAid 30-Inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Even-Heat™ True Convection and Fresh Pizza Mode

product_title.final_value: KitchenAid 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes - PrintShield™ Finish

description.final_value: Discover the KitchenAid 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven, designed for culinary enthusiasts. Featuring Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent cooking, Assisted Cooking Modes for culinary exploration, and smart capabilities for remote control. Its PrintShield™ Finish resists fingerprints, ensuring your kitchen looks immaculate.

details.final_value: This KitchenAid wall oven brings innovation to your kitchen with its smart features and unique cooking modes. The Even-Heat™ True Convection ensures precise baking, roasting, and broiling, while the Assisted Cooking Modes guide you through recipes for perfect results. Control your oven remotely with smart appliance capabilities, and enjoy the convenience of a self-cleaning system.

features_list.final_value:
• Even-heat™ true convection for consistent results
  • Assisted cooking modes for culinary exploration
  • Smart appliance capabilities for remote control
  • Self-cleaning system for easy maintenance
  • Printshield™ finish resists fingerprints
  • Air fry for healthier cooking options
  • Steam bake with tray for moist baking
  • Fresh pizza mode for restaurant-style pizzas
  • No preheat slow roast for tender meats
  • Satinglide™ roll-out extension rack for easy loading
  • Even-heat™ true convection for consistent baking and roasting results
  • Assisted cooking modes suggest ideal times and temperatures for various foods
  • Air fry function delivers crispy meals with less oil, no preheat needed
  • Smart connectivity with amazon alexa and google assistant for remote control
  • Self-cleaning cycle simplifies maintenance with steam clean option
  • Temperature probe monitors internal food temperature without opening the door
  • Fingerprint-resistant finish keeps the oven looking clean and modern
  • Sabbath mode for religious holiday cooking requirements
  • Multiple rack positions and gliding racks for easy access
  • Fresh pizza mode reaches 550°f for restaurant-quality results at home

product.description:
Stay one step ahead in the kitchen with assistive cooking methods that provide a groundbreaking smart experience and new levels of precision that help bring out the boldness in every flavor. Assisted Cook Cycles recommend the ideal cooking cycle and temperature for common foods like cake, salmon filets, roasted vegetables, and more. Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking and roasting. Temperature Probe provides internal temperature updates on oven screen without opening the door.Backlit knobs twist to navigate cook cycles and customize home screen.

Features:

  • Knob and touch controls are easy to use
  • Enjoy the convenience of self-cleaning
  • Convection baking provides even heat distribution for improved browning and crisping
  • Wall oven is certified for UL
  • Oven includes baking element, air fry, meat thermometer, steam cooking, and viewing window
  • Sabbath Mode to meet kosher requirements for use on the Jewish Sabbath and other religious holidays
  • Smooth close door makes it easy to close the oven while your hands are full with special hinges that help prevent slamming
  • FIT System Limited Guarantee
  • Assisted cooking modes suggest cook times and temperatures on an easy-to-navigate touch screen so you can explore new recipes with confidence
  • Temperature probe provides internal temperature updates on oven screen or your mobile device so you can keep the precise heat needed
  • Favorites make your favorite cooking settings easy to access by creating and saving them right in the KitchenAid™ App or directly on your appliance
  • Far View screen automatically enlarges key information like temperature or remaining time after a few minutes of inactivity
  • Covered under a 1 year parts and labor manufacturer warranty

Product Technologies:

  • Even-Heat™ True Convection: Features a unique bow-tie design with a heating element and fan that circulates hot air throughout the entire oven, providing optimal temperatures for delicious baked goods, juicy roasts and flavorful vegetables
  • Steam Bake with Tray: Adds moisture during the baking process so you can enjoy Basque cheesecake, or fluffy, moist honey wheat sandwich bread
  • Fresh Pizza Mode: Create homemade, restaurant-style pizzas from the comfort of your kitchen. Fresh pizza mode cranks the heat to 550°F for delicious results
  • No Preheat Slow Roast: Provides tender meats, pastas and much more without the hassle of a separate appliance. Plus high-temp settings for soups, medium-temp settings for braising meats and low-temp settings to keep food warm after cooking
  • SatinGlide™ Roll-Out Extension Rack: Features a roll-out extension rack and ball-bearing rollers with an easy-grip handle for effortless loading and unloading of large or heavy dishes
  • Slow Cook: Cooks food slowly at a low temperature, great for stewing meats and vegetables or building flavors in stews and currys with temperatures from 180°F to 300°F
  • No Preheat Air Fry Mode: Uses heating elements and a fan to circulate hot air within the cavity, crisping and browning food with less oil. When compared to deep frying. Dishwasher-safe basket sold separately
  • Steam Clean: Perfect for quick, routine maintenance, helps loosen cooked-on food in under an hour. Simply add water to the bottom of the oven and wipe down after the cycle
  • Self-Clean: For a deeper clean, the high-temperature Self-Clean Cycle powers through baked-on spills, leaving the oven cavity clean with just a final wipe-down

Specifications:

  • Convection: Yes
  • Self Cleaning: Yes
  • Depth: 26-15/16"
  • Height: 28-3/4"
  • Width: 29-3/4"
  • Cutout Depth: 24"
  • Cutout Height: 28"
  • Cutout Width: 28-1/2"

rawPayload.Product_Description_Web_Retailer: Explore new recipes with built-in tips on this KitchenAid smart wall oven, featuring our Most Precise Even-Heat(TM) True Convection and Assisted Cooking Modes. LED Touchscreen display and backlit knobs allow for tactile display navigation. The backlit knobs also provide a visual cue throughout the cooking process, illuminating when the oven is preheating and pulsing when cooking is finished. Designed to be personalized, these wall ovens are available in a curated palette of exterior finishes and can be customized with mixed metal hardware.
rawPayload.Product_Title_Web_Retailer: 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes - PrintShield(TM) Finish

Primary_Attributes.Description_Verified: The Kitchen. Aid 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes offers a groundbreaking smart experience and new levels of precision. Features include Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking, a temperature probe for internal temperature updates, and a variety of cooking modes to explore new recipes with confidence. The sleek stainless steel finish and Print. Shield™ resist fingerprints, ensuring your oven looks as good as it cooks.
Primary_Attributes.Product_Title_Verified: KitchenAid 30" Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes - Printshield™ Finish
Primary_Attributes.Details_Verified: This advanced KitchenAid wall oven brings smart technology and culinary precision into your kitchen. Its Even-Heat™ True Convection system ensures consistent heat distribution, while the temperature probe and assisted cooking modes make it easier to cook complex dishes. The PrintShield™ finish keeps the oven looking pristine.
Primary_Attributes.Features_List_HTML:
• Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking
  • Temperature probe for precise cooking
  • Assisted cooking modes for culinary exploration
  • PrintShield™ finish resists fingerprints
  • Smart appliance capabilities with WiFi connectivity
  • Self-cleaning and steam clean options
  • Air Fry mode for healthier cooking
  • Large capacity for big meals
  • Easy-to-use knob and touch controls
  • UL certified with a 1-year manufacturer warranty

product_title.final_value: KitchenAid 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes - PrintShield™ Finish

description.final_value: Discover new culinary adventures with KitchenAid's 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven. Equipped with Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent results, Assisted Cooking Modes for built-in recipe guidance, and a sleek PrintShield™ Finish. Features include a temperature probe, air fry mode, steam cooking, and Sabbath Mode. Control your oven through the KitchenAid™ App or with voice commands for a seamless cooking experience.

details.final_value: This KitchenAid wall oven brings modern convenience and precision to your kitchen with features like Even-Heat™ True Convection, air fry, steam cooking, and smart controls. Customize your cooking with assisted cooking modes and control your oven remotely for a seamless kitchen experience.

features_list.final_value:
• Even-heat™ true convection for consistent results
  • Assisted cooking modes with built-in recipe guidance
  • Temperature probe for precise cooking
  • Air fry mode for healthier cooking options
  • Steam cooking for moist dishes
  • Control with kitchenaid™ app or voice commands
  • Printshield™ finish resists fingerprints and smudges
  • Sabbath mode for religious observances
  • Backlit knobs and led touchscreen display for easy navigation
  • Customizable with mixed metal hardware
  • Even-heat™ true convection for uniform baking and roasting
  • Air fry mode for crispy results with less oil
  • Assisted cooking modes suggest optimal times and temperatures
  • Wifi-enabled for remote control via app
  • Steam bake function for moist, flavorful baked goods
  • Fresh pizza mode reaches 550°f for restaurant-quality results
  • Temperature probe monitors internal food temperature
  • Self-cleaning cycle for easy maintenance
  • Fingerprint-resistant finish for a sleek look
